high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and turn right to face the microwave.
Pick up the potato on the counter to the left of the microwave.

Wash the potato in the sink and remove it.
Turn to the right to face the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to the sink, then turn right and walk to the microwave.
Pick up the potato on the counter to the left of the microwave.

Put the potato in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
